    <text id="B0521T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>How's letter refers to his reports on refugees, and on lands held by his Bureau
                    office.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    Bureau <abbr expan="Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">R. F. &amp; A.
                        L.</abbr><lb/><abbr expan="Headquarters">HdQrs</abbr> Sixth <abbr
                            expan="District Virginia">Dist Va</abbr>
                    <name type="recipient"><abbr expan="Colonel">Col.</abbr> O. Brown, <abbr
                            expan="Assistant Commissioner">Asst. Comr.</abbr><lb/>Richmond, <abbr
                            expan="Virginia">Va</abbr></name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1865-09-01"><abbr expan="September">Sept</abbr> 1st 1865</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Colonel</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your copies each of the blank
                    reports of Refugees &amp;c &amp; of Lands, and in answer to the request
                    to forward the Land <abbr expan="Report">Rept</abbr> by the 5th inst have
                    respectfully to inform you that I have no Lands or Houses to report.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>I am, Colonel<lb/>Very Respectfully<lb/>Your <abbr
                            expan="Obedient Servant">Obedt Servt</abbr></salute>
                    <signed>W. Storer How, <abbr expan="Captain and Assistant Quartermaster">Capt
                            &amp; AQM</abbr><lb/><abbr expan="Superintendent">Supt</abbr> 6th
                            <abbr expan="District Virginia">Dist Va</abbr></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
